      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get the resistance thing but it feels so unnecessary when the skin is literally perfect now. like, if the bacteria are gone, the medicine is just extra stress on my liver and gut for no reason. if i just stop now, what's actually the worst that happens? it's not like i'm feeling sick anymore.",
